OL,3,CBlue Islands must compensate pilot
OL,4,Cmore than #17,000 in damages
OL,6,FA Jersey tribunal has ruled that Blue
OL,7,FIslands must pay one of its former
OL,8,Fpilots more than #17,000.
OL,10,FMark Chadwick worked as an Airline
OL,11,FCaptain for Blue Islands before their
OL,12,Fcollapse.
OL,14,FAs part of his employment, Captain
OL,15,FChadwick was required to pay a
OL,16,FTraining Bond of #20,000.
OL,18,FThe company would then reimburse him
OL,19,F#555 per month over the course of
OL,20,Fthree years.
