OL,3,CBlue Islands must compensate pilot
OL,4,Cmore than #17,000 in damages
OL,6,FHowever, when the airline went into
OL,7,Fliquidation, Captain Chadwick was
OL,8,Fterminated from his position, having
OL,9,Fonly been reimbursed #2,775.
OL,11,FThe Employment and Discrimination
OL,12,FTribunal judgement states that Blue
OL,13,FIslands has not filed a response to
OL,14,FCaptain Chadwick's claim form.
OL,16,F"As the claims are undefended, the
OL,17,FClaimant (Captain Mark Chadwick) is
OL,18,Fentitled to judgment in default,"
OL,19,FAdvocate Dr E Moran, Chairman of the
OL,20,Ftribunal board, stated.
